analysis.summary: This document is a compilation of six news articles from November 2011 covering international affairs, including US-Egypt relations during the Arab Spring, the European debt crisis, the Syrian uprising, Turkish foreign policy, Obama administration policies, and America's role in the Asian century. The articles represent analytical reporting from major media outlets on geopolitical developments.
